We are praying for all those impacted by the terrible tragedy in Florida today.

Live NOW with @Varneyco to discuss the #memo.

Tune in now!

Thank you to everyone for all the calls and sincere concern. Kelly and I were not on the train headed to the GOP retreat this morning.

Please join us in praying for all involved.
“As long as we have confidence in our values, faith in our citizens, and trust in our God, we will never fail.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“As long as we are proud of who we are, and what we are fighting for, there is nothing we cannot achieve.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"The people dreamed this country. The people built this country.  And it is the people who are making America great again.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU #MAGA

"Atop the dome of this @USCapitol stands the Statue of #Freedom. She stands tall and dignified among the monuments to our ancestors who fought and lived and died to protect her.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTUHistory
“We need only look at the depraved character of the #NorthKorea regime to understand the nature of the #nuclear threat it could pose to America and our allies.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU

“North Korea's reckless pursuit of nuclear missiles could very soon threaten our homeland. We are waging a campaign of maximum pressure to prevent that from happening.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU #NorthKorea
"But we must be clear:  #Terrorists are not merely criminals. They are unlawful enemy combatants." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“We will continue our fight until #ISIS is defeated.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU

“As part of our defense, we must modernize and rebuild our #nuclear arsenal, hopefully never having to use it, but making it so strong and powerful that it will deter any acts of aggression.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“For this reason, I am asking the Congress to end the dangerous defense sequester and fully fund our great #military.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU #SupportOurTroops
“We know that weakness is the surest path to conflict, and unmatched power is the surest means of our defense.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“Around the world, we face rogue regimes, #terrorist groups, and rivals like China and Russia that challenge our interests, our economy and our values.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“As we rebuild America’s strength and confidence at home, we are also restoring our strength and standing abroad." @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU

"My administration is committed to fighting the drug epidemic and helping get treatment for those in need. 

"The struggle will be long and difficult — but, as Americans always do, we will prevail.” @Potus @WhiteHouse #SOTU #OpioidEpidemic
“It is time to reform these outdated #immigration rules, and finally bring our immigration system into the 21st century.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU

"My duty, and the sacred duty of every elected official in this chamber, is to defend Americans -- to protect their safety, their families, their communities, and their right to the #AmericanDream." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"I want our youth to grow up to achieve great things."@POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU

“So tonight, I am extending an open hand to work with members of both parties — Democrats and Republicans — to protect our citizens of every background, color, religion and creed.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"We have proposed new legislation that will fix our #immigration laws, and support our ICE and Border Patrol Agents." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“Tonight, I am calling on the Congress to finally close the deadly loopholes that have allowed MS-13, and other criminals, to break into our country.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“As America regains its strength, this #opportunity must be extended to all citizens.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
“We can lift our citizens from welfare to work, from dependence to independence, and from poverty to #prosperity.” @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU

"Together, we can reclaim our building heritage.  We will build gleaming new roads, bridges, highways, railways, and waterways across our land.  And we will do it with American heart, American hands, and American grit." @Potus #SOTU @WhiteHouse
"America is a nation of builders." @Potus #SOTU
" As we rebuild our industries, it is also time to rebuild our crumbling infrastructure." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"The era of economic surrender is over." @POTUS #SOTU @WhiteHouse
"In our drive to make Washington accountable, we have eliminated more #regulations in our first year than any administration in history." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"I will not stop until our #veterans are properly taken care of, which has been my promise to them from the very beginning of this great journey." @POTUS #SOTU
"Americans love their country.  And they deserve a Government that shows them the same love and loyalty in return." @POTUS #SOTU
"In America, we know that faith and family, not government and bureaucracy, are the center of the American life.  Our motto is 'in God we trust.'" @POTUS #SOTU
"We all share the same home, the same heart, the same destiny, and the same great American flag." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"If you work hard, if you believe in yourself, if you believe in America, then you can dream anything, you can be anything, and together, we can achieve anything." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU

"This is our new American moment. There has never been a better time to start living the American Dream." 

@POTUS @WhiteHouse #SOTU
"Since we passed tax cuts, roughly 3 million workers have already gotten tax cut bonuses -- many of them thousands of dollars per worker." @POTUS @WhiteHouse #TaxReformWorks #SOTU
"This April will be the last time you ever file under the old broken system -- and millions of Americans will have more take-home pay starting next month." @POTUS #TaxReformWorks #SOTU
"Our massive tax cuts provide tremendous relief for the middle class and small businesses." @POTUS #SOTU #taxreform
"So let us begin tonight by recognizing that the state of our Union is STRONG because our people are STRONG." @POTUS #SOTU

"Tonight, I call upon all of us to set aside our differences, to seek out common ground, and to summon the unity we need to deliver for the people we were elected to serve. " 
@POTUS #SOTU

"With us tonight is one of the toughest people ever to serve in this House -- a guy who took a bullet, almost died, and was back to work three and a half months later:  the legend from Louisiana, Congressman @SteveScalise." @POTUS #SOTU #LouisianaStrong
"We saw the volunteers of the #CajunNavy, racing to the rescue with their fishing boats to save people in the aftermath of a devastating hurricane." @POTUS #LouisianaStrong #SOTU
What issues do you hope to hear about in tonight's #SOTU?

I have examined the classified memo from @HouseIntelComm. 

The American people deserve transparency. #ReleaseTheMemo

Want to get more information on tax reform sent to directly to you? 

Text "tax reform" to 50589!
I'm LIVE with @Varneyco to discuss tax reform and the Sessions hearing yesterday. Tune in NOW!
Joining @Varneyco this morning at 10:30 a.m. CST to discuss #TaxReform.

Another unspeakable tragedy brought about by senseless violence. 

We are praying for the victims in Las Vegas and for their families.

Joining @Varneyco this morning at 8:20 CST to discuss #HurricaneHarvey.

Continuing to pray for all affected by this devastating storm.
"Nothing can defeat the unbreakable spirit of the people of #Texas and #Louisiana." @POTUS  #HurricaneHarvy
We are shocked and saddened by the shooting this morning. We join countless Americans in praying for the victims & their precious families.

"Today we did what we had to do. They counted on America to be passive. They counted wrong." — Reagan 

#SyriaChemicalAttack #SyriaStrikes

"Believe in yourselves.

Believe in your future.

And believe, once more, in America." @POTUS #JointAddress

"We are one people, with one destiny. We all bleed the same blood.We all salute the same flag.
And we are all made by the same God." @POTUS
"To those allies who wonder what kind of friend America will be, look no further than the heroes who wear our uniform." @POTUS #JointAddress
"The challenges we face as a Nation are great.  But our people are even greater." @POTUS #JointAddress
"Our veterans have delivered for this Nation –- and now we must deliver for them." @POTUS #JointAddress
"We must provide the men & women of the U. S. military w/ the tools they need to prevent war & –- if they must –- to fight & to win." @POTUS
"We must build bridges of cooperation and trust –- not drive the wedge of disunity and division." @POTUS #JointAddress
"Every American child should be able to grow up in a safe community, attend a great school & have access to a high-paying job." @POTUS
"True love for our people requires us to find common ground, to advance the common good..." @POTUS #JointAddress
"#Obamacare is collapsing & we must act decisively to protect all Americans. Action is not a choice, it is a necessity" @POTUS #JointAddress
"Our obligation is to serve, protect, and defend the citizens of the United States." @POTUS #JointAddress
"We have undertaken a historic effort to massively reduce job‑crushing regulations." @POTUS #JointAddress
"A new chapter of America greatness is now beginning." @POTUS #Jointsession
"First & foremost we are Americans...This congress can & must play a part in restoring civility." @RepBrianFitz (R-PA) #CommitmentToCivility
"We all share a commitment to bring the voice of the American people to D.C." @RepCharlieCrist (D-FL) #CommitmentToCivility
"Civility is about the how - about our tone, about our tenor, about the words we choose to use and it's about respect. @RepBRochester (D-DE)
"We promise to put people before politics." @RepTenney (R-NY) #CommitmentToCivility
"Our ability to get things done rests on the ability to participate in productive political dialogue and discourse." @RepJasonLewis (R-MN)
"There is no doubt in my mind that there is more that unites us, than divides us." @RepCarbajal (D-CA) #CommitmentToCivility
Members of the freshman class are speaking on the House floor now on our commitment to civility in politics and debate!
